Headcount Chart

Population Definition

Global People org is defined by all HO departments what roll up to Global People function in SMART SPEND system. Thus global people associates dont include field HR associates (e.g.HR manager and training coordinator, etc.)

Turnover

In this analysis, turnover rate is defined as

\[ Turnover = \frac{Total Term}{AvgHeadcount}*100\% \]

Where

  • TotalTerm is number of associates separated during last 26 pay periods, not including transfers.
  • AvgHeadcount is the rolling average of last 26 pay periods.

Time window for this analysis is from 2020-03-13 to 2021-04-02.

Separation by EC Leaders

Description

The dataset contains associate separations for positions at Sr.director and above. There are 804 separations in total from 2019-02-01 to 2021-03-31. Both quarterly totals and 26 pay period rolling totals are calculated at the EC leader level.
